summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Greenwood Avenue from North Fiftieth Street to North Forty-first Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 17177, creating Local Improvement District No. 1614 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
